data.description: This lovely 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, single family home located in (Liberty City) Miami. Seller will give a credit of $3k at closing to repair some of the tiles. cThis homes features freshly painted inside , kitchen with granite countertops & cabinets, stainless steel appliances and a stackable washer & dryer. This homes also has all window blinds, air conditioning unit with large fenced yard great for entertaining. This home is great for investment! You can turn this home into an Air B & B. You less than 10 minutes away from Wynwood, downtown Miami, Design District, Midtown, Miami International Airport, Port of Miami, Jackson & UM Hospitals. Only 15 minutes from the Miami Beach & South Beach!! Near beaches, shopping, parks, restaurants & groceries stores. Minutes from I-95 & the 112.
